description: There was a mistake on the bass tab during the chorus. One tiny little fill was accidentally an octave too high. Whoops! I couldn't live with letting people assume it was correct, so I fixed it.
title: I Feel Bad For You

description: My first attempt was programmed like sheet music with repeats, endings, and a D.S. al Coda. After uploading to Songsterr, the order of playback got all goofed up, so I reprogrammed the song to be straight through with minimal repeats.
title: I Feel Bad For You
